-mandatory-to-prevent-random-actuation-during-mcu-boot","target":"floating-gate-pull-down-on-mosfet-is-mandatory-to-prevent-random-actuation-during-mcu-boot","line":36}],"metadata":{"description":"SRCLR (pin 10) and OE (pin 13) on the 74HC595 are both active-LOW — SRCLR must be tied HIGH for normal operation (LOW clears register) and OE must be tied LOW for outputs to work (HIGH disables them) — leaving either floating causes confusing silent failures","type":"knowledge","topics":["[[passives]]"],"source":"[[74hc595-8-bit-shift-register-serial-to-parallel-dip16]]"},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"key":"knowledge/74hc595-srclr-and-oe-are-active-low-control-pins-that-must-be-tied-correctly-or-outputs-fail-silently.md"},"smart_blocks:knowledge/74hc595-srclr-and-oe-are-active-low-control-pins-that-must-be-tied-correctly-or-outputs-fail-silently.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"r1ej1l","at":1776206766998},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.04788571,-0.0217492,0.00226886,-0.02691443,0.00447486,0.00426161,-0.04044516,0.08419748,-0.03122259,-0.03283013,0.01031294,-0.04160079,0.08629233,0.07737355,-0.01417502,0.01641419,-0.0031689,0.0312161,0.07535234,0.05306022,0.02696875,-0.00333353,-0.00395541,0.01267082,0.04378543,0.05199676,-0.05872523,-0.09340975,-0.06380941,-0.23558193,-0.03265674,0.0102592,0.03584652,0.03903936,-0.00889341,-0.06942532,-0.05868423,0.05775733,-0.0209019,0.00117423,0.03302797,-0.02102595,0.05175447,0.0172127,0.00848074,0.01089738,-0.0492054,-0.02155969,0.01601627,-0.08488099,-0.01195573,-0.00118041,-0.04068174,-0.05855834,0.00206597,-0.02155501,0.04097686,0.07584216,0.00297975,0.0257,0.05045631,0.03051735,-0.18425934,0.0267227,0.06532858,0.00572395,-0.00592088,-0.01884059,0.01047959,-0.00740762,-0.00218234,-0.02814958,-0.03460372,0.05639415,0.00430236,-0.04026169,-0.02384689,-0.02440996,-0.02624995,-0.00450341,0.01913772,-0.01475575,-0.02673911,-0.01307999,-0.07318257,-0.03581066,0.02609963,0.0178